    <item>
      <title>मन्दिर-सेवा</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/AgamaH_shaivaH/meta/mandira-sevA/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/AgamaH_shaivaH/meta/mandira-sevA/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: GA&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;dont-touch-the-vrshabha&#34;&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t touch the vRShabha&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Offer prayers to Vṛṣabha from far &amp;amp; then offer prayers to Bhagavān, followed by a method if circumbulation called somasūtra pradakṣiṇam. No touching of Vṛṣabhadeva or even stepping on his shadow or even allowing one’s shadow to mingle with Vṛṣabhadeva’s.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;somasūtra-circumbulation&#34;&gt;somasūtra circumbulation&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It should be the default because the Āgama actually advises people against crossing the gomukhī.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;thumbnail&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;../images/soma-sUtra-pradaxiNam.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;../images/soma-sUtra-pradaxiNam.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;वृषं चण्डं वृषं चैव&lt;br&gt;&#xA;सोमसूत्रं पुनर्वृषम्।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;चण्डं च सोमसूत्रं च&lt;br&gt;&#xA;पुनश्चण्डं पुनर्वृषम्।।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;इति शिवरहस्ये।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
